race.comment: JIMMY MANOLO (3) tough gelding with his hoof on the till in this easier contest. Strong through the line when fourth over 2100m at Wyong in BM64 grade. Won at the track and can get into the stalking position from the draw. Go close. STOCK ROAD (9) fourth-up today and expecting a better showing in this weaker race. Back in trip when a plugging fifth over 1600m at Wyong. Drops in weight and D-Day is looming. TYCOON LAD (10) on the quick backup after turning in a shocker when eighth over 2230m at Grafton. Assess on his good second two-back at Scone. Don't underestimate. PURPLE KITTY (4) gone to a new level this time in with the two wins from his last three starts. Jumps in trip after he demolished his rivals over 1408m at Taree. Finds a suitable race and can build on that solid recent effort.
